      <div class="msgContentFrame">Stop and think about what makes sense to use pliers for as opposed to a hammer.  Squeezing ingots into wire?  No.  Bending wire into rings?  Yes.  Linking rings together?  Yes.  Linking sheets of rings together?  Yes.  Squeezing ingots into sheets?  No. <br /> <br />Most of the offhand tools have very clear purposes.  You just have to put yourself in the position of the character doing the work and ask which tool would make sense to you.</div>
